author: @RaitoSoraTV
text: September 24, 2025... I'm here to check if this song actually reached 6 Billion. I was so surprised. I was here when this music video was first released. Like I watched this vid 20 mintues after it was initially posted publicly. The views were like around 20-30k. I was 17 years old at the time and I thought this song flopped. I remember liking it, but I just thought it flopped at the time. I do hear this occassionally being played on events and radio stations but I didn't think much of it over the years. 8 years later, I scrolled to a youtube shorts to find out that this song got 6 Billion views. I was shocked. I don't know, I find this boring story cool enough to share. It's nothing really important, it's not life changing. But the fact that I thought Shape of You flopped for 8 years straight is just bewildering to me, to say the least.

author: @stephencormie945
text: Praying Everyone has different beliefs. Some people pray and some people don't pray. I believe man is God. I believe in the universe. I also believe in the sun. The sun is a part of the universe and provides vitamin d for humans. The sun is much bigger than the earth. Also the sun provides energy for plants. The sun doesn't judge anyone, it just shows up in the sky. Also without even seeing the sun I know it's real because I can feel the heat on a hot day. The sun is very powerful. I believe the universe will provide me with what I need. The universe is big and powerful so I have faith in it. Ask the universe for what you want and put the work in when needed. So how do we pray to the universe? The universe responds to how you feel. It's really important that you feel good. The universe responds to this vibration. - Focus on what you are greatful for, including the little things. - Visualize what you want and feel yourself having it. - Think about what you want. - Write down and read about things you want. - Trust your instincts (instincts are ususally right most of the time). Trust your instincts as long as you don't hurt anyone else. - Ask the universe for what you want - Do things that make you feel great about yourself. - Do things that make you feel happy. - Make a vision board with pictures on it of things you want. - If you aren't sure what you want I recommend visualising Gold, gold is valuable. - You could also visualise golden light healing your body or something else you want (light giving you adrenaline for example) You could also visualise white light healing your body, white represents purity. - If you aren't sure what you want pray for the FEELINGS and EMOTIONS you want. - If you aren't sure what you want pray for oppotunities for the feelings and emotions you want. For example if your bored with life start praying for oppotunities to find healthy ideas for excitement. Start exploring different options and hopefully you find an exciting activity. If your angry in life work on your attitude and pray for oppotunities to find the calmness your need. Don't get desperate when praying. Pray, have faith in the universe and yourself. Yes put the work in when required, this is very important aswell. Try one or all of these ideas above and see how much better your life will become. If you have a different idea that works then great, keep using that. In times of stress do healthy and appropriate things to take your mind off the situation and improve your mood. During times of stress focus on all the little things you are greatful for. You could spend some time each day visualising what you want. There are many oppotunities to do this within the day. You could write down things you want and visualise them. You could write down things you want and imagine GOLDEN LIGHT making the things you want a reality (I recommend this if you don't know what it looks like in your mind when trying to visualise what you want). Light is very powerful and very fast. Pray in a positive way. For example instead of praying, "I don't want to see people go hungry", pray for people to have enough to eat. Instead of focusing on your debts, setup repayment plans and focus on prosperity and wealth. Some more examples I don't want to be alone, so what do you want, a companion who is good company and likes you. I don't want to be sick, so what do you want, a healthy body that is strong. I don't want the elite to control people, so what do you want, peace and love and happiness for everyone. Lets say you want a woman but don't want kids, so what do you want, a beautiful woman without kids. Don't even think about having kids if you don't want kids. Saying things in a positive way can make you feel better about the situation. You could also ask the universe for what you want. For example "Universe I want a healthy heart". Now sometimes you will feel negative during your life and this is ok. Sometimes a little negative energy or stress in the body is good to keep you motivated. Sometimes negativity and stress can be great as a warning sign, example drinking too much alcohol and having a hangover. This feeling tells the body to slow down on the alcohol. When exercising your body is put under stress but there are many health benefits associated with exercise. Now if you feel negative and stressed for too long this is not good for the body. The body and mind struggles to deal with too much negativity and stress. Trust me I know. Great examples are holding onto anger for too long about a certain issue. Also abusing drugs and alcohol puts the body and brain under lots of stress. Now when under stress I recommend trying to get happy again. Easier said than done, I know. The universe responds to how you feel and positive thoughts are much more POWERFUL than negative thoughts. For example if you are feeling bad about people suffering when watching the news, maybe don't watch the news anymore or could you work out a solution to help. If you can't do nothing to help maybe you could pray for them to get better. At the very least you could listen to some feel good music to make yourself feel better about your own life for the moment. Sometimes the best thing is to just let go of the situation and think about happy things or just move on with your life. Sometimes we can hype up things in our mind too much. If this happens maybe try to think about calming thoughts and slow your body down. Also if you want a partner and they don't want you try to let go to reduce your own stress levels. There are plenty of people in the world. If your waiting for a meal and your complaining that's what you get more of, the waiting. Why because you are focussing on the waiting. Try are focus on something positive or be thankful for the money to buy the meal. You could be thankful for other things in your life aswell. I have faith in the universe. Sometimes work is needed to change your life. Example - getting healthier and working on improving fittness Everyone needs to work no matter what the situation in life is. Controlling emotions requires work. Without good emotional control life will be tough no matter how much money you have. Great examples Rich man with drug and alcohol problems Rich man with anger or depression Rich man who suffers from boredom or lonliness Remember this statement 10 percent is the situation, 90 percent is how we react Example blaming a spouse for being lazy with household chores and getting angry at them. Maybe have a calm chat and compromise with household chores. Also a solution could be hiring a butler. Also try to appreciate the good qualities he or she has Also try to focus on things that make you feel good so you don't hold on to the anger for as long, I believe this is very important for your mental and physical health. Sometimes getting angry lets off steam, you don't always want to keep everything bottled up inside. It's ok to show emotions, it's just what we do with the emotions and how we react to these emotions that determines our quality of life in my opinion. You may not achieve everything you want or get everything you want but remember developing a strong mindest is invaluable. Having a strong mindest will help you in every situation in life I believe. How to give yourself a better chance to get what you want and have a well balanced life Being positive most of the time Visualising what you want Focusing on what you want Looking after your health Managing your emotions in a healthy way PATIENECE IS REQUIRED WHEN PRAYING TO THE UNIVERSE AND WORKING ON YOUR GOALS I BELIEVE HAVING A STRONG MINDEST IS AN ADVANTAGE IN LIFE AND GIVES YOU A MUCH BETTER CHANCE OF HAVING A WELL BALANCED LIFE Remember when you aren't feeling good it's really important to find a way to make yourself feel better (without hurting anyone else and ideally don't hurt yourself). It's even more important to keep doing the little things to improve your mood and well being. It's even more important to keep doing the little things to improve your mood and well being.

author: @thelionking219
text:
As of 2025, The Metro Tunnel was completed which included twin 9 km rail tunnels between South Kensington and South Yarra, 5 new underground stations at Arden, Parkville, State Library, Town Hall and Anzac and it has the Sunbury, Cranbourne and Pakenham lines running through it. Also it has direct airport connection via the Melbourne Airport Rail Link which was completed in 2029 and included an upgraded Sunshine Station with a new regional platform and a new transport superhub, a rebuilt Albion Station on ground level on the Sunbury Line, a new Keilor East Station on ground level and a new elevated Melbourne Airport Station on skyrail.

And as of 2043, the Suburban Rail Loop was completed which is a 90 km rail line from Cheltenham to Werribee via Melbourne Airport and 60 kms of it from Cheltenham to Melbourne Airport was built underground with 13 new underground stations at Cheltenham, Clayton, Monash, Glen Waverley, Burwood, Box Hill, Doncaster, Heidelberg, Bundoora, Reservoir, Fawkner, Broadmeadows and Melbourne Airport, 2 new transport superhubs at Clayton and Broadmeadows and SRL driverless trains.

author: @thelionking219
text:
On the South Morang Line as of 2018, the Mernda Rail Extension from South Morang to Mernda was completed and it included 3 new stations at Middle Gorge, Hawkstowe and Mernda. Middle Gorge Station was built on ground level and Hawkstowe and Mernda Stations were built above ground with skyrail. And that train line is now called the Mernda Line.

And as of 2019, the level crossing at High Street, Reservoir was removed by building a 1 km skyrail with a new elevated Reservoir Station.

Then, as of 2022, the 4 level crossings at Oakover Road, Bell Street, Cramer Street and Murray Road in Preston were removed by building a 2 km skyrail with 2 new elevated stations at Bell and Preston.

And then, as of 2024, the level crossing at Keon Parade, Keon Park was removed by building a 750 m skyrail with a new elevated Keon Park Station.

author: @thelionking219
text:
As of 2025, The Metro Tunnel was completed which included twin 9 km rail tunnels between South Kensington and South Yarra, 5 new underground stations at Arden, Parkville, State Library, Town Hall and Anzac and it has the Sunbury, Cranbourne and Pakenham lines running through it. Also it has direct airport connection via the Melbourne Airport Rail Link which was completed in 2029 and included an upgraded Sunshine Station with a new regional platform and a new transport superhub, a rebuilt Albion Station on ground level on the Sunbury Line, a new Keilor East Station on ground level and a new elevated Melbourne Airport Station on skyrail.

And as of 2043, the Suburban Rail Loop was completed which is a 90 km rail line from Cheltenham to Werribee via Melbourne Airport and 60 kms of it from Cheltenham to Melbourne Airport was built underground with 13 new underground stations at Cheltenham, Clayton, Monash, Glen Waverley, Burwood, Box Hill, Doncaster, Heidelberg, Bundoora, Reservoir, Fawkner, Broadmeadows and Melbourne Airport, 2 new transport superhubs at Clayton and Broadmeadows and SRL driverless trains.

author: @thelionking219
text:
On the South Morang Line as of 2018, the Mernda Rail Extension from South Morang to Mernda was completed and it included 3 new stations at Middle Gorge, Hawkstowe and Mernda. Middle Gorge Station was built on ground level and Hawkstowe and Mernda Stations were built above ground with skyrail. And that train line is now called the Mernda Line.

And as of 2019, the level crossing at High Street, Reservoir was removed by building a 1 km skyrail with a new elevated Reservoir Station.

Then, as of 2022, the 4 level crossings at Oakover Road, Bell Street, Cramer Street and Murray Road in Preston were removed by building a 2 km skyrail with 2 new elevated stations at Bell and Preston.

And then, as of 2024, the level crossing at Keon Parade, Keon Park was removed by building a 750 m skyrail with a new elevated Keon Park Station.

author: @desmay2studios
text:
Listened to Ed a lot in my teens. X came out when I was 11, and while I liked music a lot at the time (I grew up on Snow Patrol, A Hundred Million Suns is still my favourite album of all time) Multiply is the album that made me absolutely fall in love with music. It made me want to learn how to play guitar, write songs, and sing (2/3 so far lol, can't sing to save my life). His concert here in Brisbane in 2015 was my first concert.

Since then, I've taken in a lot of different styles and influences, expanded my listening tastes quite a lot. Every now and again, I still find myself coming back to Ed's music and absolutely loving it, it's so nice to hear his voice and melodies.
Play is a gorgeous album. Absolutely love it, even if it's a polar opposite to the type of music I tend to listen to these days.
